name: tesla_roadster
description: The Tesla Roadster is a high-performance all-electric sports car that can seat up to four passengers. It has a starting price of $200,000 and a range of 620 miles.

name: tesla_model_s
description: The Tesla Model S is a full-size all-electric luxury sedan that can seat up to five passengers. It has a starting price of $74,500 and a range of 335 miles.

name: tesla_model_x
description: The Tesla Model X is a midsize all-electric luxury SUV that can seat up to seven passengers. It has a starting price of $65,500 and a range of 295 miles.

name: tesla_model_3
